OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry and cloudy start
OL,6,Ffor many. The cloud will soon thin and
OL,7,Fbreak up to give some prolonged spells
OL,8,Fof sunshine during the afternoon.
OL,9,FGenerally, a touch warmer compared to
OL,10,FMonday, with mainly light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry with variable
OL,13,Fcloud and clear spells inland.
OL,14,FBecoming cloudier in the east,
OL,15,Fespecially along the coasts and on
OL,16,Fhills. Light and variable winds. A
OL,17,Fmild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
