OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start in places,
OL,6,Fespecially along the coasts, with
OL,7,Fperhaps the odd spot of light rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle. Otherwise, dry with variable
OL,9,Fcloud and warm sunny spells. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith variable cloud and bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells Thursday. Similar
OL,15,Fconditions Friday, but breezier. A
OL,16,Fband of rain moves southeast on
OL,17,FSaturday. Temperatures will be nearer
OL,18,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
